contentOffer.title: BMW Drive Recorder
contentOffer.shortDescription: You get the picture: With the BMW Drive Recorder you can film beautiful landscapes as well as dangerous or critical driving situations in road traffic.
contentOffer.longDescription:
WHAT IS THE BMW DRIVE RECORDER?
Automatically or manual activation the BMW Drive Recorder films your surroundings for up to 40 seconds. This allows you to document dangerous driving situations in road traffic. With the BMW Drive Recorder, you can also collect wonderful memories of beautiful routes at the press of a button. Four integrated cameras mean that it is easy to shoot videos.

The features described here may not be fully supported in all markets. May only be available with additional optional equipment. Availability of BMW ConnectedDrive Services are dependent on vehicle specification, optional equipment and production date. Please consult your local BMW Retailer for more information if required.
  • Up to 40 seconds of video footage of your surroundings.
  • Automatic activation is triggered in the event of an accident.
  • Videos can also be saved manually at the press of a button.

contentOffer.title: Remote Engine Start
contentOffer.shortDescription: With the new Remote Engine Start feature, your BMW will always be at the temperature you want when you get in  and it is super easy to use.
contentOffer.longDescription:
WHAT IS REMOTE ENGINE START?

With the Remote Engine Start feature, you can bring the interior of your BMW to the temperature you want at any time, even if you yourself are somewhere completely different. You can program this feature from the sofa at home, at the office, or while sitting in a restaurant.  The Remote Engine Start feature starts your BMW's engine and air-conditioning system before you leave completely automatically.

  • Your vehicle already at the desired temperature when you get in.
  • Easy to operate with the BMW Connected app and the BMW Display Key.
  • Versatile and secure thanks to the automatic switch-off.
